<p>留学生们参观成都蜀锦织绣博物馆</p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201021/b3f5d1fdd13d4992a757ff72335db2ae.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
